[
    {
        "text": "Humans once wielded formidable magical power.",
        "source": "api",
        "start_time": 0.0,
        "end_time": 0.0,
        "start_progress": 0.0,
        "end_progress": 0.015492957746478873
    },
    {
        "text": "But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect.",
        "source": "api",
        "start_time": 0.0,
        "end_time": 0.0,
        "start_progress": 0.01584507042253521,
        "end_progress": 0.05070422535211268
    },
    {
        "text": "When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.",
        "source": "api",
        "start_time": 0.0,
        "end_time": 0.0,
        "start_progress": 0.051056338028169015,
        "end_progress": 0.09507042253521127
    },
    {
        "text": "This is a story of the end of the world, and the beginning of the next.",
        "source": "api",
        "start_time": 0.0,
        "end_time": 39.0,
        "start_progress": 0.0954225352112676,
        "end_progress": 0.12077464788732395
    },
    {
        "text": "John was the second generation to start to have noticeable powers.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 39.0,
        "end_time": 52.0,
        "start_progress": 0.12112676056338029,
        "end_progress": 0.1443661971830986
    },
    {
        "text": "It was almost something that he had taken for granted, as he did not know what it was like before to have none.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 52.0,
        "end_time": 83.0,
        "start_progress": 0.14471830985915493,
        "end_progress": 0.18380281690140846
    },
    {
        "text": "There were now classes in the little school to teach the children how to harness their Mana and use it, in the hopes that one day a generation would be strong enough to take back their home.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 83.0,
        "end_time": 108.0,
        "start_progress": 0.1841549295774648,
        "end_progress": 0.251056338028169
    },
    {
        "text": "John was now in his final year of school, and was one of the stronger students.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 108.0,
        "end_time": 134.0,
        "start_progress": 0.25140845070422535,
        "end_progress": 0.2795774647887324
    },
    {
        "text": "While he was stronger, he was still not considered unusual, as there had been far more impressive people he had learned about in his history class.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 134.0,
        "end_time": 167.0,
        "start_progress": 0.27992957746478875,
        "end_progress": 0.3316901408450704
    },
    {
        "text": "He didn't know that one day that was about to change and he could hold the key to restoring order on his earth.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 167.0,
        "end_time": 186.0,
        "start_progress": 0.33204225352112676,
        "end_progress": 0.3711267605633803
    },
    {
        "text": "He was a tall, well-built young man with short brown hair and a friendly face.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 186.0,
        "end_time": 201.0,
        "start_progress": 0.3714788732394366,
        "end_progress": 0.39929577464788735
    },
    {
        "text": "Nothing that spoke to the powers that were laying in wait inside him.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 201.0,
        "end_time": 224.0,
        "start_progress": 0.3996478873239437,
        "end_progress": 0.423943661971831
    },
    {
        "text": "It was during a practice exercise that he began to feel different.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 224.0,
        "end_time": 235.0,
        "start_progress": 0.4242957746478873,
        "end_progress": 0.44753521126760565
    },
    {
        "text": "The goal was to either provide a shield around yourself, or blast away a fake alien that was in the fight room.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 235.0,
        "end_time": 266.0,
        "start_progress": 0.447887323943662,
        "end_progress": 0.4869718309859155
    },
    {
        "text": "A good student could be fairly impressive at one, although no one was really that great.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 266.0,
        "end_time": 291.0,
        "start_progress": 0.48732394366197185,
        "end_progress": 0.5183098591549296
    },
    {
        "text": "The instructors hoped that with practice though, the children would be powerful enough when they grew up to serve the security force well.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 291.0,
        "end_time": 318.0,
        "start_progress": 0.518661971830986,
        "end_progress": 0.5672535211267605
    },
    {
        "text": "Suddenly it was John's turn.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 318.0,
        "end_time": 324.0,
        "start_progress": 0.5676056338028169,
        "end_progress": 0.5778169014084507
    },
    {
        "text": "He felt a cold stillness take over his body that he had never felt before.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 324.0,
        "end_time": 335.0,
        "start_progress": 0.578169014084507,
        "end_progress": 0.604225352112676
    },
    {
        "text": "And then suddenly it exploded around him.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 335.0,
        "end_time": 343.0,
        "start_progress": 0.6045774647887324,
        "end_progress": 0.6190140845070422
    },
    {
        "text": "The fake alien flew back against the wall with such force that it clattered to the ground in pieces.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 343.0,
        "end_time": 361.0,
        "start_progress": 0.6193661971830986,
        "end_progress": 0.6545774647887324
    },
    {
        "text": "But not only that, there was now a distinctive blue shield around John.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 361.0,
        "end_time": 375.0,
        "start_progress": 0.6549295774647887,
        "end_progress": 0.6799295774647888
    },
    {
        "text": "He had done both.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 375.0,
        "end_time": 199.0,
        "start_progress": 0.680281690140845,
        "end_progress": 0.6862676056338028
    },
    {
        "text": "The instructors were stunned.",
        "source": "api",
        "start_time": 199.0,
        "end_time": 388.0,
        "start_progress": 0.6866197183098591,
        "end_progress": 0.6971830985915493
    },
    {
        "text": "No one could speak.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 388.0,
        "end_time": 392.0,
        "start_progress": 0.6975352112676056,
        "end_progress": 0.704225352112676
    },
    {
        "text": "Finally they told John to release his shield and shower and get ready for his next class.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 392.0,
        "end_time": 408.0,
        "start_progress": 0.7045774647887324,
        "end_progress": 0.7359154929577465
    },
    {
        "text": "By the time he went home and had dinner for his family, he had forgotten about his display, but the school had not.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 408.0,
        "end_time": 425.0,
        "start_progress": 0.7362676056338028,
        "end_progress": 0.7767605633802817
    },
    {
        "text": "There was a knock at the door and the headmaster and the head of security were ushered into the sitting room.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 425.0,
        "end_time": 442.0,
        "start_progress": 0.777112676056338,
        "end_progress": 0.8154929577464789
    },
    {
        "text": "They conferred with John's parents for quite some time.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 442.0,
        "end_time": 386.0,
        "start_progress": 0.8158450704225352,
        "end_progress": 0.8352112676056338
    },
    {
        "text": "\"John, we have some good news for you,\" his father said.",
        "source": "api",
        "start_time": 386.0,
        "end_time": 474.0,
        "start_progress": 0.8355633802816902,
        "end_progress": 0.8556338028169014
    },
    {
        "text": "\" You are going to be given an opportunity that most can only dream of.\"",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 474.0,
        "end_time": 491.0,
        "start_progress": 0.8559859154929578,
        "end_progress": 0.8820422535211268
    },
    {
        "text": "\"You are going to the capital\" There were tears in his father's eyes but pride in his voice.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 491.0,
        "end_time": 507.0,
        "start_progress": 0.8823943661971831,
        "end_progress": 0.9144366197183098
    },
    {
        "text": "And John knew that while it was called an opportunity, he was not being given a choice.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 507.0,
        "end_time": 524.0,
        "start_progress": 0.9147887323943662,
        "end_progress": 0.9454225352112676
    },
    {
        "text": "His life path had been decided for him.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 524.0,
        "end_time": 531.0,
        "start_progress": 0.9457746478873239,
        "end_progress": 0.9595070422535211
    },
    {
        "text": "And while he was scared he was also excited.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 531.0,
        "end_time": 545.0,
        "start_progress": 0.9598591549295775,
        "end_progress": 0.9753521126760564
    },
    {
        "text": "He packed his bags and wondered how he would ever sleep that night.",
        "source": "user",
        "start_time": 545.0,
        "end_time": 470.0,
        "start_progress": 0.9757042253521127,
        "end_progress": 0.9992957746478873
    }
]